  RECOMMENDATION: Python performance is acceptable.
    No Rust migration needed at current scale.

  Rust migration priority (if needed):
    1. SecurityScannerRule (shared by all rules)
    2. RefactoringRule (hot-path rules)
    3. DebugCleaner (high-frequency rules)
